      "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body" : "Seems like I was fixing a problem that did not exist in the first place.  I will be closing this PR for the sake of resubmitting another one which should reflect non-standard use of Script in a warning fasion rather than error and terminate.\n\nBoth non-minimally encoded numbers /and/ wasteful pushes are valid in blocks.  Thanks @sipa for clarifying.\n",
